insert mode special key
CTRL-O insert mode execute a single vim command
CTRL-H == del
CTRL-W == del word <-
CTRL-J == CTRL-M begin new linhe
CTRL-R insert reg 
CTRL-T add a shift >
CTRL-D del a shif
CTRL-G j down line
CTRL-G k up line



